Required Libraries: 
=====================
1. Download and install cvblob from here: http://code.google.com/p/cvblob/
For installation instruction, read the README file in cvblob.


How to run rviz and gazebo:
============================
 roslaunch youbot_description youbot_description.launch 
 roslaunch youbot_description youbot_publisher.launch (starts gazebo)

 roslaunch youbot_navigation_local move_base_local.launch (start navigation)

 rosrun rviz rviz


